name: Steve Hobbs
tweet: I'm proud of the more than 380 service members I command, who run more than 20 food banks, warehouses and distribution centers in Western WA. We've processed, packaged and delivered more than 30 million lbs of food for Washingtonians in need. Your Guard helping our communites.
